---
title: Glazed Pork Meatballs & Kūmara Wedges with Cucumber Salad
description: Oh, happy days! With a heavenly combination of a crisp green salad, served alongside kūmara wedges and a sticky-sweet cherry glaze slathered over pork meatballs, this is a modern and delicious union that will be happily devoured by all.
